Section A: Exploratory Data Analysis

Data Quality # Foreclosures is a wide data set where NA means the property is not foreclosed and 1 = foreclosed.

When comparing this brief analysis of Detroits Property Assessment Data, the first impression of the data when only looking at the means is that properties generally are being assessed at a lower value than their sale price.
